original: Lindberg, Paul Johannes, kyrkoherde, Nårunga, f. 30/9/99 i Böne, Älvsb. 1., av Gustav L. o. Hilda Petersson. G. 33 m. Brita Helde. Barn: Ulla f. 34, Gert 35, Ann-Sofie 38. — Stud:ex. i Skara 17, teol. fil. ex. 19, teol. kand. samt prakt. teol. prov 27, prästv. f. Skara stift 28. V. pastor i Blidsberg 28, v. kommin. i Borås 30, kyrkoh. i Nårunga sed. 32.
translated: Lindberg, Paul Johannes, clergyman, Nårunga, b. 30/9/1899 in Böne, Älvsb. 1., son of Gustav L. and Hilda Petersson. Married in 1933 to Brita Helde. Children: Ulla b. 1934, Gert b. 1935, Ann-Sofie b. 1938. Completed secondary education in Skara in 1917, theological degree in 1919, theological candidate and practical theological examination in 1927. Ordained as priest for the Skara diocese in 1928. Assistant pastor in Blidsberg from 1928, assistant vicar in Borås from 1930, vicar in Nårunga from 1932.
